    <events>
        <after_init>
            <dialog>
                <title>Doran</title>
                <talks>
                    <talk>
                        You! Help me, please!
                    </talk>
                    <talk>
                        I know, I shoudn't be here, but someone told me I could find jewels in this place...
                    </talk>
                    <talk>
                        But I never heard there were zombies of any kind around here!
                    </talk>
                    <talk>
                        I don't care about your business, but save me and I'll offer you my services.
                    </talk>
                </talks>
            </dialog>
        </after_init>
        <at_end>
            <dialog>
                <title>The village is safe</title>
                <talks>
                    <talk>
                        Only a few seconds after you placed the remains back on the altar you hear some weird noises...
                    </talk>
                    <talk>
                        All the undeads in the crypt are crumbling into dust.
                    </talk>
                    <talk>
                        You assume it's the same for those who are outside.
                    </talk>
                    <talk>
                        Thanks to your intervention, the villagers have been saved and the peace should be back in Nervie.
                    </talk>
                    <talk>
                        You are now on your way to the town, thinking of the reward promised by the innkeeper.
                    </talk>
                </talks>
            </dialog>
        </at_end>
